headline: Deutsche Bank Lifts PT on Monster Beverage Corporation (MNST) to $88 From $84
summary: Monster Beverage Corporation (NASDAQ:MNST) is one of the best sugar stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On February 20, Deutsche Bank lifted the price target on Monster Beverage Corporation (NASDAQ:MNST) to $88 from $84 while keeping a Buy rating on the shares. In a separate development, Argus raised the price target on the stock […]
